Under Digital Unix 4.0E (formerly DEC OSF/1):
$ uname
OSF1
$ cd /tmp
$ mkdir TT
$ cd TT
$ rmdir .
rmdir: .: Invalid argument
$ rmdir /tmp/TT
$ ls -a
. not found
$ ls -a /tmp/TT
/tmp/TT not found
$ pwd
pwd: read error in ..
$ cd ..
..: No such file or directory
$
--Scott
